================================================================================
Model serving — managed STACKIT AI Model Serving (no bundled weights)
================================================================================

Inference runs entirely on the managed, EU-sovereign STACKIT AI Model Serving
API via LiteLLM — a three-tier set: reasoning (Qwen/Qwen3-VL-235B-A22B-Instruct-FP8,
LiteLLM sovereign-reasoning), standard/worker (openai/gpt-oss-20b, sovereign-default)
and embeddings (Qwen/Qwen3-VL-Embedding-8B, sovereign-embed). No model engine or
model weights are bundled or redistributed as part of this product. On kind/local
the bundled mock-model (our own Apache-2.0 image) serves deterministic offline
embeddings only.

